This value set contains 8 concepts

DataAbsentReason

Used to specify why the normally expected content of the data element is missing

This value set defines its own terms in the system http://hl7.org/fhir/data-absent-reason

CodeDisplayDefinitionv3 Map (NullFlavor)
unknown UnknownThe value is not known=UNK
asked AskedThe source human does not know the value=ASKU
temp TempThere is reason to expect (from the workflow) that the value may become known=NAV
notasked NotaskedThe workflow didn't lead to this value being known=NASK
masked MaskedThe information is not available due to security, privacy or related reasons=MSK
unsupported UnsupportedThe source system wasn't capable of supporting this element>NA
astext AstextThe content of the data is represented in the resource narrative
error ErrorSome system or workflow process error means that the information is not available>NA
